Package: textpress
Type: Package
Title: "A lightweight & versatile NLP companion in R."
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jason Timm [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jason Timm <JaTimm@salud.unm.edu>
Description: Provides features for (1) basic text processing, (2) corpus search, and (3) web scraping.  Additionally included are utility functions for (4) building text embeddings via the HuggingFace API, and (5) fetching chat completions via the OpenAI API.  
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    httr,
    Matrix,
    rvest,
    stringi, 
    stringr,
    xml2,
    pbapply,
    jsonlite,
    lubridate
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
URL: https://github.com/jaytimm/textpress, https://jaytimm.github.io/textpress/
BugReports: https://github.com/jaytimm/textpress/issues
